                           <item>
                              <seg type="subject">Gold 4-line initial with vine-stem decoration on a multicoloured ground.</seg>
                           </item></list>
                           </decoNote><decoNote type="border">Fine historiated border.
                              <list type="gloss">
                           <label>Type</label>
                           <item>
                              <seg type="genreform">border, upper, left and lower margin</seg>
                           </item>
                           <label>Subject</label>
                           <item>
                              <seg type="subject">The border is formed by double gold bars and vine-stem decoration on a multicoloured ground, with an owl, peacock (?) and gold disks. At the bottom of the page two winged putti support a laurel wreath with the coat of arms of Francesco Sassetti.</seg>
                           </item>
                        </list></decoNote><decoNote type="decInit">3- to 4-line gold initials and borders in left and upper margins, formed by sprays of flowers, leaves, fruit and gold disks, on fols. 14r, 138r, 190r. Border on fol. 14r includes an elaborate urn.
                     </decoNote>
                  </decoDesc>
